* Install TFT_eSPI & LVGL libraries & 

///////////////////////////////////////////////////////
//             TFT_eSPI Library setiing              //
///////////////////////////////////////////////////////

* Open your Arduino IDE folder in this folder find the libraries and in this libabry open TFT_eSPI 
* In TFT_eSPI folder open User_Setup.h file un comment your disply driver or if you want to use existing setup than open User_Setup_Select.h file and uncomment your driver
* Than go to User_setup folder in tihs folder find your driver name .h file and adujust pin or other setting according to sutible your project and device
NOTE:- this project using <User_Setups/Setup70d_ILI9488_S3_Parallel.h>  with esp 32s3-Wroom-1 and ILI9488 Display 


///////////////////////////////////////////////////////
//             LVGL Library setiing                  //
///////////////////////////////////////////////////////

* Open LVGL lilibabry and open this and in this folder find lv_conf_template.h file remane with lv_conf.h and copy this file and finde scr folder and past this file 
* Open lv_conf.h Set it to "0" tp "1" for enable content 
* if you want to use Littlefs in Arduino ide with lvgl than find LV_USE_FS_ARDUINO_ESP_LITTLEFS set "0" to "1" and Set an upper cased letter on which the drive will accessible
* for use png & decode for this LV_USE_LODEPNG is enabel and also if you want to use bmp file enabel LV_USE_BMP 
* and if you using existing TFT_eSPPI disply setting finde LV_USE_TFT_ESPI  and set "0" to "1"

==> link for image and font convert for lvgl 
   for image: https://lvgl.io/tools/imageconverter
   for font : https://lvgl.io/tools/fontconverter
